            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Your memo was supposed to be around here... Right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes. However, I've forgotten exactly where. I only recall the general area..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha... Then let's take a little look around."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I'm sorry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Wow, this book is full of tags..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Ah, that was me. I feel discomfort unless I tag everything that I find even remotely interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hm? Wait, this is... Plachta's diary! Let's see, what does it say..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x20,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "N-no, Sophie! I won't allow even you to read that!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Darn it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Memo, where's that memo... Ah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hey! Could this be the memo?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "...Yes, it would seem so. How very nostalgic..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It was difficult coming up with that recipe, but those days were most fulfilling."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Huh... Then I guess this memo is full of memories for you, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I'll use it with care."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Yes, please do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Alright! Now then... Let's hurry back to the atelier and Synthesize it!"
